SimpleRF:
Minimum communication, test if my hardware is ok.

turnOnOff:
A basic software whic tests to turn on the motor pump by switching the relay

turnOnOff_RF:


turnOnOff_RFv2:
Controller sends an integer variable beginnig from 1 , every cycle
the pump node takes the received integer variable and turns the pump on.
The integer variable are the amount of time to turn on the pump.


turnOnOff_RFv3:
Same as turnOnOff_RFv2, but the PumpNode goes into sleep mode and wakes up 
if a message arrives, so we care about interrupts
